## Dot lang. {#dot-lang-dot}

```dot
graph graph1 {
      something;
}
```


### indirected {#indirected}

```dot
graph graph1{
      a -- b -- c;
      b -- d;
      }
```


### directed {#directed}

```dot
digraph graph1{
	a -> b -> c;
	b -> d;
	}
```


### attrs {#attrs}

```dot
strict graph{
       // node attr
       b [shape = box];
       // edge attr
       a -- b [color=blue,style = dotted];
       }
```


### subgraph {#subgraph}

```dot
digraph graphname{
    a -> {b c};
    c -> e;
    b -> d;

    subgraph cluster_bc {
	bgcolor=red;
	b;
	c;
    }

    subgraph cluster_de {
	label="Block"
	d;
	e;
    }
}
```


## Use {#use}


### in Shell {#in-shell}

```sh
dot -Tpdf filename.dot > filename.pdf
```